  "",
  "As documents were distributed, Shi moved closer to Wang.",
  "“Professor Wang, I understand you’re researching some kind of … new material?”",
  "",
  "“Nanomaterial,” Wang answered.",
  "",
  "“I’ve heard of it.",
  "That stuff is really strong, right?",
  "Do you think it could be used to commit crimes?”",
