  "“You’re right.",
  "Even a fish can be used to commit a crime.",
  "I handled a murder case once.",
  "Some bitch cut off her husband’s family jewels.",
  "You know what she used?",
  "A frozen tilapia she got out of the freezer!",
  "The spines along the back were like razors—”",
  "",
  "“I’m not interested.",
  "Did you ask me to the meeting just to talk about this?”",
  "",
  "“Fish?",
  "Nanomaterials?",
  "No, no, nothing to do with those.”",
  "Shi put his mouth next to Wang’s ear.",
  "“Don’t be nice to them.",
